data.description: * Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this inviting two-story townhome * Boasting 3 bedrooms and 1 1/2 bathrooms, this residence features newer luxury vinyl flooring on the main floor, adding a touch of modern elegance * Step into the open living room, warmed by a wood-burning fireplace, creating a cozy atmosphere for gatherings * The spacious dining area seamlessly connects to the efficiently laid-out kitchen, equipped with new countertops, a self-cleaning oven/range, built-in microwave oven, dishwasher, disposal, and refrigerator * A guest half bath and main floor laundry area provide added convenience * Ascend the staircase to find three bedrooms, including a master bedroom with two closets for ample storage * One of the secondary bedrooms easily accommodates two twin beds * The full bathroom, positioned at the top of the stairs, ensures accessibility for all bedrooms, complemented by two linen closets * Outside, the courtyard between the townhouse and detached two-car garage offers a safe space for pets and children to enjoy the outdoors * A spacious deck and patio provide ideal spots for outdoor entertaining * Nestled in the Hallcrafts Village East Community, residents enjoy access to a clubhouse and community pool, surrounded by greenbelts * Friendly neighbors and community events organized by the HOA, including festive holiday parties, enhance the sense of community * Your dues cover trash pickup every Monday and efficient snow removal, ensuring a hassle-free living experience * With school choice options, a variety of schools are within reach * Shopping, churches, and gyms are conveniently located, completing the picture of a well-rounded and comfortable lifestyle * Welcome home!
